List::Part version 0.01
=======================

List::Part implements the C<part> function, allowing one array to be 
"partitioned" into several based on the results of a code reference.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None.

